                | (くるえりと繋ぐ御縁音源) ライブ会場で1円で販売中
            .col-md-8
              iframe(scrolling="no" id="hearthis_at_track_1037427" width="100%" height="150" src="https://hearthis.at/embed/1037427/transparent_black/?hcolor=&color=&style=2&block_size=2&block_space=1&background=1&waveform=0&cover=0&autoplay=0&css=" frameborder="0" allowtransparency)
          .row.bottom10px
